CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1959, pg. 28, reads: "Winner - A. J. Scott, left, winner of the cent Pittsburgh Courier groundhog derby, gives with a big grin as he receives a Remington shotgun from Chester Neft of Sol's Stores in Wilkinsburg. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Courier Groundhog Derby prizewinner A. J. Scott receiving Remington shotgun from Chester Neft, in Sol's Store, Wilkinsburg
